      <abstract id="aspace_cf1e2203bfb6d944d34a8b0cdaaf9944">The collection contains the autograph books of Brooklyn residents Sue Gilmore, Miriam Miller, Frank Pergolizzi, Daisy, Martha, and Louise Baldwin, as well as the autograph book and wedding cards of Edna West, and an unidentified autograph book. They document the friendships and relationships of Brooklyn men and women from the mid 1870s to the 1920s, often containing personal notes and scraps documenting school life.</abstract>
      <langmaterial id="aspace_22832d5dfcb1ed39755de7d8cbd9cf2f">All materials are in English.</langmaterial>
    </did>
